  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "……すず。記事を読んでみてくれる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Suzu. Can you read the article?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "わ、分かりましたわ。ええと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "O-Okay. Let's see…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "『長く停滞が続いた月のテンペストだが\nようやく力強いステージを見せてくれた』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Moon Tempest‚ which has been stagnant for a long time‚\nfinally showed a powerful stage",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "『しかし彼女達の道のりはまだまだ険しい\nライブバトルの成績や人気の回復……』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But their path is still steep\nLive battle results and popularity recovery…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "『中でも一番の課題は、センターの長瀬琴乃だ』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The biggest challenge is the center‚ Kotono Nagase",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.3443570455
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "な、なんですの、この言い方は！\n琴乃を一体なんだと……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-What's with this wording!\nHow dare they talk about Kotono like that…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "すず、ありがとう\n……続きは、私が読むから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu‚ thank you\n…I'll read the rest",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "え？　でも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? But…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫、ありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's okay‚ thank you",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.3
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "『デビュー直後は輝くものがあり、頂点を狙える凄みを\n感じられたが、I-UNITY以降精彩を欠いている』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right after her debut‚ there was something shining‚ and you could feel\nthe potential to aim for the top‚ but since I-UNITY‚ she's lost her luster",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "『ⅢXへの敗北がよほどトラウマになっているのか\nかつてのようなキレがなくなった』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whether the defeat against ⅢX was that traumatic‚\nshe's lost the edge she once had",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "『このままでは、その他大勢の中に埋もれるだろう』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At this rate‚ she'll be buried among the masses",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん……真に受けることないよ\n今日の琴乃ちゃん、とっても凄かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono… Don't take it to heart\nToday‚ Kotono‚ you were really amazing",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 78.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "そうですわ！　この無責任な記事を書いた人は\n琴乃のことをなんっっっにも分かってませんわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right! The person who wrote this irresponsible article\nDoesn't know aaanything about Kotono!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 86.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "センターに立ち続けるプレッシャーも知らずに……\nよくもこんなことを……っ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Without knowing the pressure of continuously being the center…\nHow dare they say such things…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.3
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "すずにゃん、落ち着いて！　どーどー！\n……でも、芽衣も同じ気持ちだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu-nyan‚ calm down! Take it easy!\n…But‚ Mei feels the same way",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "確かに最近はちょっと調子が悪かったけどさ\n今日のライブは最高だったでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sure‚ we've been in a bit of a slump lately\nBut wasn't today's live the best?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "月ストのステージを観てくれた人がさ……\nみーんなとっても素敵な笑顔になってたよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The people who watched Moon Tempest's stage…\nThey all had such wonderful smiles!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "そうですよ。練習だって沢山積んで、冷静に見ても\nI-UNITYの時より実力はずっと伸びてます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. We've practiced a lot‚ and objectively speaking\nOur skills have improved a lot since I-UNITY",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "今なら……スリクスとだって\n互角か、それ以上に戦えると思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now… I think we can fight\nOn equal terms with ⅢX‚ or even better",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "今日、ステージを観てくれた人はみな\nはっきりと月ストを応援してくださっていましたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone who watched our stage today\nWas clearly cheering for Moon Tempest",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "外からいろいろ言う人達にはさ、これから先\n文句を言えないくらい凄いステージを見せちゃおうよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's show those people who say various things from the outside\nA stage so amazing they won't be able to complain anymore!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_04-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "ネットでの評価は確かに胸に刺さりますが……\nそれでも気にしている時間はありませんよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The online evaluations certainly sting…\nBut we don't have time to worry about that",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
